(7, 'Chat Support Agent', 'Kochi', '', 'Full-Time', NULL, '1 year', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">We are seeking dedicated and customer-focused individuals to join our team as Chat Agents. As a Chat Agent, you will be responsible for providing exceptional customer service and support through online chat platforms. Your primary goal will be to engage with customers, address their inquiries, and deliver prompt and accurate solutions.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Responsibilities:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Respond promptly and professionally to customer inquiries through chat platforms.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Provide accurate information regarding products, services, and company policies.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Assist customers with product selection, order placement, and issue resolution.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Engage in proactive communication to upsell or cross-sell relevant products or services.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Requirements:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">High school diploma or equivalent; further education is a plus.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Proven customer service experience, preferably in a chat-based support role.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Excellent written and verbal communication skills.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Proficient in typing with a high level of accuracy.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Ability to multitask and prioritize workload effectively.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Familiarity with CRM systems and chat platforms is a plus.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Flexibility to work in rotational shifts, including weekends and holidays.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Ability to work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environment.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Positive attitude, patience, and empathy towards customers.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Join our team as a Chat Agent and contribute to providing exceptional customer experiences. Apply today with your updated resume and cover letter detailing your relevant experience and skills.</span></p>', '2023-06-21', 'chat-support-agent'),
(8, 'Business Analyst', 'Sydney', '', 'Full-Time', NULL, '2 years', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">We are seeking a highly skilled and detail-oriented CRM Business Analyst to join our team. As a CRM Business Analyst, you will play a crucial role in optimizing our customer relationship management system and processes. Your primary responsibility will be to gather and analyze business requirements, identify system improvements, and collaborate with cross-functional teams to implement CRM solutions that drive operational efficiency and enhance customer experiences.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Responsibilities:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Collaborate with stakeholders to gather and document business requirements related to CRM processes and functionalities.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Conduct detailed analysis of current CRM system and processes to identify areas for improvement and optimization.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Perform data analysis to identify trends, patterns, and insights that can inform CRM strategies and decision-making.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Develop and maintain comprehensive documentation, including business process flows, use cases, and functional specifications.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Collaborate with IT teams to translate business requirements into technical specifications and ensure successful system implementation.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Provide end-user training and support during CRM system implementations and enhancements.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Stay up-to-date with industry trends and best practices in CRM and recommend innovative solutions to drive continuous improvement.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including sales, marketing, and customer service, to ensure CRM system aligns with business objectives.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Requirements:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Bachelor\'s degree in Computer Science, or a related field.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Proven experience as a Business Analyst, with a focus on CRM systems and processes.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to gather and interpret complex data sets.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Proficiency in CRM software (e.g., Salesforce, Microsoft Dynamics, Oracle CRM) and related tools.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Excellent documentation and communication skills, with the ability to effectively present complex concepts to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Knowledge of CRM best practices and industry trends.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Strong project management skills with the ability to handle multiple tasks and deadlines.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Collaborative mindset with the ability to work effectively in cross-functional teams.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Attention to detail and a commitment to delivering high-quality work.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">If you are a highly motivated and detail-oriented professional with a passion for CRM and driving business success, we invite you to apply for the role of CRM Business Analyst. Please submit your resume, detailing your relevant experience and accomplishments in CRM analysis and implementation.</span></p>', '2023-06-21', 'business-analyst'),
(9, 'Sales Manager', 'Sydney', '', 'Part-Time', NULL, '3 years', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">We are seeking a dynamic and results-driven Sales Manager. As a Sales Manager, you will be responsible for leading our sales team, driving revenue growth, and fostering strong client relationships. Your primary focus will be on acquiring new clients, expanding our customer base, and achieving sales targets.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Responsibilities:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Develop and execute strategic sales plans to achieve company sales targets and revenue goals.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Lead and manage a high-performing sales team, providing guidance, coaching, and motivation to drive individual and team success.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Identify new business opportunities and potential clients through market research, networking, and prospecting activities.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Build and nurture relationships with key decision-makers and stakeholders to understand their business needs and position our IT consulting services as solutions.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Prepare and present compelling sales proposals, pitches, and presentations to prospective clients, effectively communicating the value and benefits of our services.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Collaborate with internal teams, including technical experts and project managers, to ensure seamless delivery of services and client satisfaction.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Monitor market trends, competitor activities, and industry developments to identify opportunities for business growth and stay ahead of the competition.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Maintain accurate sales forecasts, pipeline management, and activity records using CRM software.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Negotiate and close sales agreements, contracts, and pricing terms to meet revenue objectives while ensuring profitable margins.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Continuously assess sales strategies, processes, and performance metrics to drive continuous improvement and achieve sales targets.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Requirements:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Bachelor\'s degree in Business Administration, Marketing, or a related field.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Proven experience as a Sales Manager or in a similar sales leadership role within the IT consulting or technology industry.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Strong track record of achieving and exceeding sales targets and driving revenue growth.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Excellent interpersonal and communication skills, with the ability to build rapport, negotiate effectively, and deliver persuasive presentations.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Strong leadership abilities, with a demonstrated ability to motivate and manage a sales team to achieve exceptional results.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Deep understanding of the IT consulting industry, market dynamics, and trends.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Ability to analyze market data and leverage insights to develop targeted sales strategies and business development plans.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Proficiency in using CRM software and sales analytics tools.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Strong business acumen and strategic thinking abilities.</span></li><li><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">Ability to thrive in a fast-paced and target-driven environment.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:hsl(0, 0%, 30%);\">If you are a dynamic and driven sales professional with a passion for IT consulting and a proven ability to lead high-performing teams, we invite you to apply for the position of Sales Manager. Please submit your resume, along with a cover letter highlighting your relevant experience and accomplishments in sales leadership within the IT consulting industry.</span></p>', '2023-06-21', 'sales-manager');

