(21, 'Automotive', '<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">The automotive industry has been revolutionized with the integration of digital technologies. With the rise of automation and digitalization, companies are looking to improve their efficiency, productivity, and customer service. Our company provides various services to support the automotive industry\'s digital transformation.&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"image image-style-align-right\"><img src=\"https://www.entsglobal.com/application/views/admin/includes/uploads/252695293automotive-content1.webp\"></figure><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\"><strong>Conversational AI</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Conversational AI can be used in the automotive industry to provide better customer service and support. It can help customers with queries and provide personalized assistance. Some specific applications of Conversational AI in the automotive industry are:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Chatbots for customer service and support</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Personalized recommendations for customers</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Predictive maintenance alerts</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Automated scheduling for service appointments</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Process identification: The first step in the process assessment is to identify the business process to be automated. The process should be well defined, documented, and standardized to ensure a successful automation outcome.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\"><strong>CRM Services</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">CRM services