(33, 'Consulting', '', '', '<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">At our company, we offer a comprehensive range of CRM consulting services to help businesses optimize their customer relationship management systems and improve customer engagement. Our team of experienced CRM consultants works closely with businesses to identify pain points in their existing CRM strategies and design customized solutions to address them.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Our CRM consulting services include a wide range of offerings, including system selection, implementation, customization, and ongoing support. We work with businesses to identify the CRM system that best aligns with their unique needs and implement it seamlessly into their operations. We also offer customization services to ensure that the CRM system is tailored to each business\'s specific workflows and processes.</span></p><figure class=\"image image-style-align-center image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img src=\"https://www.entsglobal.com/application/views/admin/includes/uploads/1199501299consulting-content1.webp\"></figure><div class=\"page-break\" style=\"page-break-after:always;\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&nbsp;</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">In addition to system selection and implementation, our CRM consulting services also include ongoing support and training. Our team of experts is available to provide troubleshooting and technical support whenever businesses need it. We also provide training services to ensure that employees know how to use the CRM system effectively and maximize its benefits.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">We understand that every business is unique, and our CRM consulting services are designed to reflect that. We work closely with businesses to develop customized solutions that are tailored to their specific needs and goals. Our goal is to help businesses optimize their CRM systems and achieve long-term success through improved customer engagement and satisfaction.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">There are several compelling reasons why businesses should consider implementing a CRM system:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Increased ROI:</strong> Implementing a CRM system can result in a significant return on investment (ROI) for businesses. Studies have shown that the average ROI for CRM implementation is $8.71 for every dollar spent.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Improved Customer Engagement and Retention:</strong>&nbsp; A CRM system enables businesses to track customer interactions and preferences, allowing them to build stronger relationships with their customers and provide better service. This leads to improved customer engagement and retention, resulting in increased revenue and profitability.</span></li></ul><div class=\"page-break\" style=\"page-break-after:always;\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&nbsp;</span></div><figure class=\"image image-style-align-right\"><img src=\"https://www.entsglobal.com/application/views/admin/includes/uploads/2064246096consulting-content2.webp\"></figure><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Increased Sales:</strong> A CRM system can help businesses identify sales opportunities, track leads and prospects, and create targeted marketing campaigns. This can lead to more effective sales and marketing efforts and higher conversion rates, ultimately resulting in increased revenue and a positive ROI.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Reduced Costs:</strong> A CRM system can help businesses streamline their workflows and automate tasks, which can reduce the time and resources needed to complete them. This can lead to cost savings and a positive ROI.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Better Decision Making:</strong> A CRM system can provide businesses with valuable insights into customer behavior and preferences. This can help businesses make more informed decisions about product development, marketing strategies, and customer service, leading to a positive ROI.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Centralized Data Management:</strong> CRM systems provide a central location for businesses to store and manage customer data. This can help businesses avoid duplicate data entry and maintain data accuracy and consistency.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\"><strong>Enhanced Productivity:</strong> A CRM system can help businesses save time and increase productivity by automating tasks and workflows. This can result in higher output and a positive ROI.</span></li></ul>', 24, 'CRM Consulting | ENTS Global', 'CRM Consulting | ENTS Global', 'CRM Consulting | ENTS Global', 'pack_628118548.webp', 'consulting', '', '', 0, 'pack_1698178786.webp', '<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">We provide businesses with expert guidance on selecting the right CRM solution for their needs, customizing it to fit their business processes, and optimizing its performance. Our team of CRM consultants has extensive experience working with leading CRM platforms, including Salesforce, Microsoft Dynamics, and HubSpot. From CRM implementation and customization to data management and process automation, we offer end-to-end consulting services to enhance customer engagement, streamline operations, and unlock valuable insights.&nbsp;</span></p>', 5, 1),
(34, 'Implementation', '', '', '<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">We understand that implementing a new CRM system can be a daunting task for businesses of all sizes. That\'s why we offer comprehensive CRM implementation services designed to help businesses seamlessly integrate a new CRM system into their operations.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Our team of experienced CRM implementation specialists works closely with businesses to understand their unique needs and goals. We take a customized approach to CRM implementation, tailoring our services to meet the specific requirements of each business.</span></p><div class=\"page-break\" style=\"page-break-after:always;\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&nbsp;</span></div><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"image image-style-align-left\"><img src=\"https://www.entsglobal.com/application/views/admin/includes/uploads/920548311implementation-content1.webp\"></figure><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">CRM implementation services begin with a comprehensive assessment of the business\'s existing workflows and processes. From there, we develop a detailed implementation plan that outlines the steps required to integrate the new CRM system into the business\'s operations. Our team works closely with businesses throughout the implementation process to ensure that everything is running smoothly and that the new system is fully integrated into their operations.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">We also offer extensive training and support services to help businesses get the most out of their new CRM system. Our team provides in-depth training to employees to ensure that they understand how to use the system effectively and maximize its benefits. We also offer ongoing technical support and troubleshooting services to ensure that businesses can quickly resolve any issues that may arise.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Overall, our CRM implementation services are designed to help businesses seamlessly integrate a new CRM system into their operations and achieve long-term success through improved customer engagement and satisfaction.</span></p>', 24, 'CRM Implementation | ENTS Global', 'CRM Implementation | ENTS Global', 'CRM Implementation | ENTS Global, integration to erp', 'pack_1250583991.webp', 'implementation', '', '', 0, 'pack_1896295787.webp', '<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:hsl(0,0%,30%);\">Our CRM Implementation service helps businesses successfully deploy and integrate their CRM solutions, ensuring a smooth transition and minimal disruption to their operations. Our expert team of CRM consultants understands the unique needs of your organization and works closely with you to design, configure, and deploy CRM systems that align with your objectives. We use a proven methodology that includes project planning, data migration, configuration, customization, and testing to ensure that the CRM system is set up correctly and ready for use.</span></p>', 6, 1),
(35, 'Production Support and Maintenance', '', '', '<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">We understand that implementing a CRM system is just the first step in a long-term strategy for success. That\'s why we offer CRM Production Support and Maintenance services to help our clients keep their systems running smoothly and effectively.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">Our team of experienced professionals provides comprehensive support and maintenance services to ensure that our clients\' CRM systems are always up-to-date and optimized for peak performance.&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:100%;\"><img src=\"https://www.entsglobal.com/application/views/admin/includes/uploads/467649782production-support-and-maintenance-content2.webp\"></figure><div class=\"page-break\" style=\"page-break-after:always;\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&nbsp;</span></div><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\">We offer a range of services to meet the unique needs of each client, including:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\"><strong>Ongoing Technical Support:</strong> Our team is available to answer any technical questions and provide support as needed to ensure the smooth functioning of our clients\' CRM systems.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\"><strong>Regular Maintenance:</strong> We provide regular maintenance services to keep our clients\' CRM systems up-to-date and running at optimal performance levels.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\"><strong>Upgrades and Enhancements:</strong> We work closely with our clients to identify areas for improvement and provide upgrades and enhancements to their CRM systems as needed.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#4d4d4d;\"><strong>System Monitoring and Reportin